{"type":"message","id":"ebcbe2c5","parentId":"9c826e08","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:07:01.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have good search results. Let me also search for smart security and IT operations services trends, then compile the learning notes.\n\nKey findings from the search:\n1. **北京2026年新政**：最高支持500万元鼓励平台赋能与数字化转型，单个平台企业最高可获500万元支持\n2. **工信部政策**：加快推进更多的工业园区企业数字化改造（2026-03-24中国政府网）\n3. **北京目标**：2026年底力争全面实现规上制造业企业数字化转型达标\n4. **2026企业数字化趋势**：数商云AI智能体引领\"智能体生态\"新赛道，多智能体协作构建企业数字生态新范式\n\n\n5. **软件定制化**：2026年企业软件从标准化向定制化转变，标志着企业数字化正从生存可选题升级为必答题\n\nNow I'm looking into smart security and IT operations services to complete the research.","thinkingSignature":"6e3ea4a4a6e6b20c280524dab9c475b58866c1bd1fa795802bb705dd21ec4b03"},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me search for smart security (智能安防) trends as well:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_azv72vinmyb7_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","profile":"openclaw","targetId":"5DA135CCFF3BE69782EE13F66347805E","url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=智能安防+2026+最新趋势+政策"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29146,"output":294,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73421,"cost":{"input":0.0087438,"output":0.0003528,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01041603}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775023609540}}
